 W-182 resolved resonance parameter evaluation was done in the    7431 1451
energy range form 1e-5 eV to 10 keV with the SAMMY code[ref1].    7431 1451
Capture and transmission measurements for enriched W-182 and      7431 1451
natural tungsten were used in the evaluation. The measurements    7431 1451
were done at the Oak Ridge Linear Accelerator (ORELA)[ref2] and   7431 1451
at the Geel Linear Accelerator (GELINA), Belgium[ref3]. Neutron   7431 1451
transmission and capture data were measured in the energy range   7431 1451
from 20 eV to 10 keV.                                             7431 1451
 Thermal cross section[ref4] data available in the EXFOR library  7431 1451
were also used in the evaluation.                                 7431 1451
                                                                  7431 1451
